<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="load-n">load <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ləʊd/    美 /loʊd/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>负载 (物)；负荷：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The trucks waited at the warehouse to pick up their loads. 
货车在仓库等着装货。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>工作量；负担：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have a <strong>full load</strong> of work. 
我的工作安排得满满的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She is under great pressure from <strong>heavy</strong> study <strong>loads</strong>.
面对沉重的学业负担，她压力很大。</p></div>

<h4 id="3burden">3.<strong>负担；压力(burden)</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When someone is depressed, the extra <strong>load of</strong> having financial problems can make the situation worse.
当一个人抑郁时，额外的经济负担会使情况变得更糟。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="get-a-load-of">get a load of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[非正式用语] 注意；仔细地看 / 听</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="loads-of-a-load-of">loads of / a load of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>很多：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There are loads of great places to see in Australia. 
在澳大利亚有很多值得一看的好地方。</p><footer>北师大④ – 12</footer></div></div>